Code for Image up-down motion:

Add (imagefloat) class to the image advance and in CSS Classes.
If you dont have pro then add below code in Customise > Additional CSS 

.imagefloat {
    animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
	0% {
		transform: translate(0, 0);
	}
	50% {
		transform: translate(0, -50px);
	}
	100% {
		transform: translate(0, 0);
	}
}
